1
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:34,918
=Vanished Name=

2
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:37,894
=Episode 8=
(Ms. Zhou's Pen)

3
00:01:38,552 --> 00:01:40,192
Your job is not easy at all.

4
00:01:40,752 --> 00:01:43,713
The bones were sealed in concrete.
Where would you find any clues?

5
00:01:43,713 --> 00:01:45,240
It's like a needle in a haystack.

6
00:01:45,953 --> 00:01:48,912
Yeah, even if it's a needle
in a haystack, we have to find it.

7
00:01:49,073 --> 00:01:51,873
So, it'd be great
if someone could provide some clues.

8
00:01:52,272 --> 00:01:54,392
Actually, I mean to give you some clues.

9
00:01:55,153 --> 00:01:59,433
Ms. Zhou gave that pen
to both Bai Shu and me back then.

10
00:02:07,593 --> 00:02:10,393
Zhou Yun gave that pen to both of you?

11
00:02:10,873 --> 00:02:11,912
You and Bai Shu?

12
00:02:12,192 --> 00:02:14,713
Yeah, that's why
I recognized it at first glance.

13
00:02:16,993 --> 00:02:18,393
So where is the pen now?

14
00:02:19,113 --> 00:02:20,273
I honestly don't remember.

15
00:02:21,352 --> 00:02:23,952
It's been too long. I probably lost it.

16
00:02:26,632 --> 00:02:28,033
Why aren't you eating?

17
00:02:28,472 --> 00:02:30,632
This steak is the best
in all of Qingzhou.

18
00:02:48,553 --> 00:02:49,192
(Ms. Zhou.)

19
00:02:49,593 --> 00:02:51,873
(2004, Qidaohezi Qidian Middle School)
Why did you come on the weekend?

20
00:02:52,113 --> 00:02:53,273
To keep you company.

21
00:02:53,873 --> 00:02:56,672
Perfect timing.
I have something to give you.

22
00:03:02,792 --> 00:03:05,993
This pen means a lot to me.

23
00:03:06,993 --> 00:03:10,113
It was a gift from
the most important person in my life.

24
00:03:10,352 --> 00:03:14,472
She asked me to give this pen
to my best student,

25
00:03:14,672 --> 00:03:19,033
so they have the strength and courage
to overcome any hardship.

26
00:03:25,752 --> 00:03:27,113
I want to give it to you two.

27
00:03:30,993 --> 00:03:33,153
But there's only one pen.
How do we share it?

28
00:03:34,033 --> 00:03:36,472
Well, that's for you two to decide.

29
00:03:59,433 --> 00:04:00,593
We can share ownership.

30
00:04:02,273 --> 00:04:06,393
When one needs courage,
the other brings the pen to her.

31
00:04:11,352 --> 00:04:12,873
Yeah, best friends

32
00:04:13,232 --> 00:04:17,753
always rush to each other's side
for support when needed.

33
00:04:23,872 --> 00:04:24,953
- Thank you, Ms. Zhou.
- Thank you, Ms. Zhou.

34
00:04:56,753 --> 00:04:58,992
Ren Xiaoming, what's wrong with you?

35
00:04:59,153 --> 00:05:00,513
- What?
- You said you went to the bathroom

36
00:05:00,713 --> 00:05:02,488
and actually paid the bill, didn't you?

37
00:05:03,393 --> 00:05:05,713
It's just a meal. Are you serious?

38
00:05:05,713 --> 00:05:07,672
Yeah, I am. I'll pay you later.

39
00:05:08,312 --> 00:05:09,513
What a bummer.

40
00:05:09,792 --> 00:05:12,232
We have disciplines.
Show some understanding.

41
00:05:12,232 --> 00:05:12,792
Fine.

42
00:05:12,912 --> 00:05:13,412
Oh, right.

43
00:05:13,492 --> 00:05:16,153
I'll send you
Bai Shu's WeChat contact later.

44
00:05:16,312 --> 00:05:19,153
Whether to add her or not is up to you.

45
00:05:19,513 --> 00:05:24,713
But I think that after all these years,
you two should clear the air, right?

46
00:05:25,153 --> 00:05:25,753
Alright.

47
00:05:26,432 --> 00:05:27,833
Okay, that's it. I'm off.

48
00:05:28,352 --> 00:05:29,193
- Bye.
- Drive safely.

49
00:05:30,393 --> 00:05:30,893
Bye.

50
00:05:30,953 --> 00:05:31,453
Bye.

51
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:47,695
(Li Meng: Money transfer)

52
00:05:47,695 --> 00:05:49,240
(Recommended WeChat contact: Shu)

53
00:05:50,193 --> 00:05:51,112
(Bai Shu.)

54
00:05:52,024 --> 00:05:55,020
(Recommended WeChat contact: Shu)

55
00:05:55,864 --> 00:05:57,073
(2004, Qidaohezi)

56
00:05:57,073 --> 00:05:59,352
I can't forget the keys
inside the house again.

57
00:05:59,992 --> 00:06:02,912
You promised you'd wake me
when the Morning Star rose.

58
00:06:03,033 --> 00:06:04,153
Why didn't you wake me?

59
00:06:05,312 --> 00:06:06,833
I'm basically home. Go back.

60
00:06:07,432 --> 00:06:09,153
We're almost there.
Let me walk you home.

61
00:06:09,672 --> 00:06:11,513
What if you twist your ankle
on the stairs?

62
00:06:12,352 --> 00:06:15,073
That's less terrifying
than my mom's beating.

63
00:06:16,432 --> 00:06:17,953
Would she even be up this early?

64
00:06:19,073 --> 00:06:21,513
True, they went
to the carnival yesterday.

65
00:06:21,992 --> 00:06:24,073
They should still be asleep
after all that fun.

66
00:06:25,033 --> 00:06:27,992
But my mom is super sneaky.
She finds out everything I do.

67
00:06:28,792 --> 00:06:29,513
Here's a trick.

68
00:06:29,753 --> 00:06:31,593
Take off your shoes, sneak inside,

69
00:06:31,912 --> 00:06:32,753
and rush to bed.

70
00:06:33,593 --> 00:06:34,552
Not here.

71
00:06:34,552 --> 00:06:35,953
- It's too cold here.
- It's fine.

72
00:06:43,833 --> 00:06:44,992
- Bye, Auntie.
- Mom.

73
00:06:47,633 --> 00:06:48,352
Mom.

74
00:06:49,153 --> 00:06:51,953
Why did he bow?
Paying respects to the deceased?

75
00:06:52,472 --> 00:06:54,672
Like that? Want me to bow to you too?

76
00:06:55,513 --> 00:06:57,312
Ren Meiyan, you're forever remembered.

77
00:06:57,953 --> 00:07:00,312
Keep talking, and I'll beat you.

78
00:07:05,833 --> 00:07:07,713
Where did you two go last night?

79
00:07:09,633 --> 00:07:11,312
You went to the carnival yesterday.

80
00:07:11,713 --> 00:07:15,153
I forgot my keys
and couldn't even get into the house.

81
00:07:15,713 --> 00:07:16,912
Darn carnival.

82
00:07:17,393 --> 00:07:19,112
Yuanyuan wanted to go with her mom.

83
00:07:19,513 --> 00:07:21,833
Mr. Sun gave the tickets to his ex-wife.

84
00:07:22,953 --> 00:07:23,992
So where did you go?

85
00:07:24,153 --> 00:07:27,753
Xiaofei had a fever and got
an IV drip in the hospital all night.

86
00:07:27,833 --> 00:07:29,953
He slept with his head on my arm.
It's killing me.

87
00:07:31,472 --> 00:07:35,393
You're both here?
What happened last night?

88
00:07:35,953 --> 00:07:39,153
Some girl was banging
on your door for long

89
00:07:39,472 --> 00:07:41,232
and kept shouting, "Ren Xiaoming.

90
00:07:41,432 --> 00:07:42,753
Ren Xiaoming."

91
00:07:42,992 --> 00:07:45,432
I couldn't sleep the whole night.
What was that about?

92
00:07:46,393 --> 00:07:47,033
Who was it?

93
00:07:48,273 --> 00:07:50,513
A pretty young girl. Very good-looking.

94
00:07:52,112 --> 00:07:53,033
Bai Shu.

95
00:07:54,073 --> 00:07:55,552
Where are you going? Tell me

96
00:07:55,552 --> 00:07:56,912
where you were last night.

97
00:07:56,912 --> 00:07:58,593
- Awful neighbors.
- Stop running.

98
00:08:10,792 --> 00:08:11,672
Bai Shu.

99
00:08:12,912 --> 00:08:14,593
Bai Shu, come out.

100
00:08:18,153 --> 00:08:19,273
Bai Shu.

101
00:08:20,713 --> 00:08:23,393
Bai Shu, come out.

102
00:08:24,672 --> 00:08:25,432
Bai Shu.

103
00:08:32,273 --> 00:08:33,192
Auntie.

104
00:08:34,153 --> 00:08:36,552
Xiaoming, what's wrong?

105
00:08:38,592 --> 00:08:39,273
Hello, Auntie.

106
00:08:39,792 --> 00:08:40,473
Hello.

107
00:08:40,633 --> 00:08:41,832
I'm here for Bai Shu.

108
00:08:43,912 --> 00:08:48,432
She's sick and won't be
going to school for a while.

109
00:08:49,312 --> 00:08:50,672
She's sick?

110
00:08:51,712 --> 00:08:52,952
How did she get sick?

111
00:08:53,993 --> 00:08:55,512
The entrance exam is coming up soon.

112
00:08:56,033 --> 00:08:56,993
Should I check on her?

113
00:08:58,393 --> 00:09:00,473
No need. She just fell asleep.

114
00:09:01,753 --> 00:09:04,273
Don't ring the doorbell again.
You'll wake her up.

115
00:09:06,672 --> 00:09:07,432
Goodbye.

116
00:09:09,473 --> 00:09:09,993
Auntie.

117
00:09:12,993 --> 00:09:14,513
Could you give this to her?

118
00:09:31,873 --> 00:09:32,552
Okay.

119
00:09:33,753 --> 00:09:34,672
No problem.

120
00:09:35,273 --> 00:09:35,993
Go home.

121
00:09:37,552 --> 00:09:38,633
Goodbye, Auntie.

122
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:37,049
(2023, Qingzhou)

123
00:11:47,072 --> 00:11:51,353
(Enter Password)
(20040601. I will remember this day.)

124
00:11:52,672 --> 00:11:55,192
(When my best friend needed help,)

125
00:11:56,792 --> 00:11:57,832
(I wasn't there.)

126
00:12:00,504 --> 00:12:01,209
(Adding friend)

127
00:12:01,209 --> 00:12:04,152
(I'm Ren Xiaoming.)

128
00:12:06,072 --> 00:12:06,808
(I missed you.)

129
00:12:10,616 --> 00:12:14,609
(Add me.)

130
00:12:23,512 --> 00:12:26,295
(Add me.)

131
00:12:38,296 --> 00:12:42,360
(Yicheng Police Station)

132
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:43,513
(Investigation area)

133
00:12:43,513 --> 00:12:44,952
Officer, sorry for the trouble.

134
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:48,780
(Iron-clad ideals, responsibilities,)

135
00:12:48,780 --> 00:12:49,848
(skills, and conduct)

136
00:12:52,672 --> 00:12:53,312
Officer.

137
00:12:53,792 --> 00:12:54,832
No more fighting.

138
00:12:55,033 --> 00:12:56,952
Okay. We're just good friends
messing around.

139
00:12:59,113 --> 00:12:59,613
Thanks.

140
00:12:59,792 --> 00:13:00,792
Where are you going?

141
00:13:02,033 --> 00:13:03,353
The car isn't here yet. Sit.

142
00:13:15,552 --> 00:13:17,353
You didn't spout any nonsense, did you?

143
00:13:18,192 --> 00:13:19,353
Like what?

144
00:13:20,153 --> 00:13:23,273
The nurse is your witness.
Whatever I say makes no difference.

145
00:13:24,753 --> 00:13:26,473
I had no choice.

146
00:13:27,113 --> 00:13:29,113
It's because you tried to kick me out.

147
00:13:29,633 --> 00:13:30,912
Kick you out?

148
00:13:33,113 --> 00:13:34,633
Be decent, alright?

149
00:13:36,233 --> 00:13:38,552
Meiyu Bainian was a huge company.

150
00:13:38,993 --> 00:13:42,873
The stock price plummeted 33 percent
in a day due to an infringement lawsuit.

151
00:13:43,592 --> 00:13:45,592
The cash flow dried up.
The company was sold.

152
00:13:46,952 --> 00:13:51,113
If you weren't popular, fine.
But you're popular right now.

153
00:13:51,153 --> 00:13:55,592
The stocks of those platform publishers
will take a hit because of you.

154
00:13:56,113 --> 00:13:58,192
Shouldn't I give them a heads-up?

155
00:14:01,273 --> 00:14:06,113
Could you give me a heads-up
before giving everyone else one?

156
00:14:06,153 --> 00:14:06,912
I...

157
00:14:08,113 --> 00:14:10,633
You said it yourself.
I'm popular right now, right?

158
00:14:12,233 --> 00:14:13,113
We are...

159
00:14:14,552 --> 00:14:16,192
We are business partners.

160
00:14:16,912 --> 00:14:19,513
If something happens,
they'll kick me out.

161
00:14:19,513 --> 00:14:22,113
What do you get
if they terminate the contract?

162
00:14:22,712 --> 00:14:28,393
Without me, could you afford
your fancy watch and fine clothes?

163
00:14:28,633 --> 00:14:31,353
You made a mistake.
Face the consequences.

164
00:14:31,952 --> 00:14:33,113
Why should I?

165
00:14:33,353 --> 00:14:36,473
Even if you get me arrested,
plenty of others will come after you.

166
00:14:36,592 --> 00:14:37,993
What do you gain from my downfall?

167
00:14:38,993 --> 00:14:42,753
Besides, I didn't call the police
to have you arrested.

168
00:14:43,233 --> 00:14:46,033
I wanted you to cool down
and think about our partnership.

169
00:14:49,432 --> 00:14:50,393
Enough.

170
00:14:52,633 --> 00:14:53,792
I've figured out a plan.

171
00:14:55,233 --> 00:14:56,248
Trying to fool me again?

172
00:14:56,832 --> 00:14:58,273
It was you fooling me.

173
00:14:59,633 --> 00:15:00,153
Come closer.

174
00:15:02,192 --> 00:15:03,192
Want to hear it or not?

175
00:15:10,273 --> 00:15:13,153
(An anonymous person revealed Writer
Liu Xiaoran suffered domestic violence.)

176
00:15:13,153 --> 00:15:16,184
(With visual proof, his wife's family
has a history of hereditary illness.)

177
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:20,536
(Preliminary diagnosis
of the People's Hospital: Schizophrenia)

178
00:15:26,473 --> 00:15:27,312
(That's terrible.)

179
00:15:27,312 --> 00:15:28,473
(No full name?)

180
00:15:28,592 --> 00:15:29,592
(Comments)
(Is the medical record fake?)

181
00:15:29,592 --> 00:15:30,353
(What's going on?)

182
00:15:30,353 --> 00:15:31,993
(Ren Xiaoming looks crazy.)

183
00:15:32,312 --> 00:15:34,153
(She hit her husband way too hard.)

184
00:15:34,153 --> 00:15:35,353
(Crazy family.)

185
00:15:35,353 --> 00:15:38,592
(Ren Xiaoming is really sick.
How could she hit such a good man?)

186
00:15:38,712 --> 00:15:40,233
(Poor Liu Xiaoran.)

187
00:15:57,912 --> 00:16:01,113
Ren Xiaoming, come find me, now!

188
00:16:08,672 --> 00:16:09,993
- Ren Xiaoming.
- You scared me.

189
00:16:09,993 --> 00:16:12,033
Didn't I tell you to lie low
before the trial?

190
00:16:12,113 --> 00:16:14,312
Why did you tell Chen Junhang?

191
00:16:14,513 --> 00:16:17,473
My bad. But he provoked me first.

192
00:16:17,993 --> 00:16:20,513
I just got carried away
and blurted it out.

193
00:16:20,712 --> 00:16:22,712
So pig-headed.

194
00:16:24,033 --> 00:16:24,952
Stay away from me.

195
00:16:25,873 --> 00:16:28,753
Do you have any idea how damaging
a PR crisis is right before a trial?

196
00:16:29,153 --> 00:16:33,312
First, the video of you
breaking Liu Xiaoran's nose went viral.

197
00:16:33,432 --> 00:16:38,952
Then there were rumors about you
having a hereditary mental illness.

198
00:16:39,592 --> 00:16:43,952
Where did they even get
the medical records?

199
00:16:44,033 --> 00:16:46,113
My brother
came to Qingzhou for treatment.

200
00:16:46,473 --> 00:16:48,633
Liu Xiaoran got him
the specialists back then.

201
00:16:49,672 --> 00:16:51,273
Liu Xiaoran is quite something.

202
00:16:51,672 --> 00:16:54,353
I'm telling you,
if it wasn't done by his team,

203
00:16:54,473 --> 00:16:56,432
I-I'll eat these cabinets.

204
00:16:56,513 --> 00:16:59,353
Don't swear oaths carelessly.
What if it really wasn't done by him?

205
00:16:59,353 --> 00:17:00,832
Are you really going to eat cabinets?

206
00:17:01,513 --> 00:17:04,592
My goodness, you still have the mood
to joke around here?

207
00:17:04,993 --> 00:17:07,993
Do you know how much impact
public opinion will have on you?

208
00:17:08,552 --> 00:17:09,993
I know. I saw it.

209
00:17:09,993 --> 00:17:12,832
What can they say about me?
That I'm abnormal.

210
00:17:12,953 --> 00:17:15,112
That I'm crazy. So what?

211
00:17:15,513 --> 00:17:18,273
Do you think
the word "crazy" has no power?

212
00:17:20,753 --> 00:17:21,473
It's my mom.

213
00:17:23,872 --> 00:17:24,392
Mom.

214
00:17:24,713 --> 00:17:27,673
Xiaoming, your brother got into a fight.
The police took him.

215
00:17:30,352 --> 00:17:32,872
(Criminal Investigation Unit)
Captain Li, we found a new lead.

216
00:17:33,713 --> 00:17:37,753
We found a complaint letter
written by Ge Wenjun in 2004.

217
00:17:38,112 --> 00:17:38,872
About whom?

218
00:17:39,513 --> 00:17:41,632
Zhou Yun, Bai Shu's homeroom teacher.

219
00:17:42,753 --> 00:17:44,552
She accused her
of falsifying her diplomas.

220
00:17:46,072 --> 00:17:47,632
And the outcome
of Educational Council?

221
00:17:47,632 --> 00:17:49,713
Zhou Yun's diplomas
were found to be valid.

222
00:17:50,552 --> 00:17:52,993
It was determined
to be a malicious accusation.

223
00:17:53,673 --> 00:17:57,072
October 21, 2004.

224
00:17:58,033 --> 00:18:03,152
According to school records,
Zhou Yun left by the end of September.

225
00:18:03,433 --> 00:18:06,913
So Ge Wenjun filed the complaint
after Zhou Yun left, right?

226
00:18:07,673 --> 00:18:08,173
Yeah.

227
00:18:08,473 --> 00:18:09,392
It makes no sense.

228
00:18:10,233 --> 00:18:12,632
Why didn't she report it
when Zhou Yun was still there?

229
00:18:13,792 --> 00:18:14,352
Yeah.

230
00:18:16,993 --> 00:18:19,913
What are you scratching your head about?
Spit it out.

231
00:18:20,312 --> 00:18:21,193
I mean...

232
00:18:22,152 --> 00:18:27,832
The complaint letter
was sent after Zhou Yun left, right?

233
00:18:28,872 --> 00:18:30,233
There are two possibilities.

234
00:18:31,033 --> 00:18:34,392
First possibility is that Ge Wenjun
didn't know Zhou Yun had already left.

235
00:18:34,592 --> 00:18:36,753
She thought she was still at school.

236
00:18:37,352 --> 00:18:38,993
Second possibility is that

237
00:18:39,352 --> 00:18:45,312
Ge Wenjun wanted to create the illusion
that she didn't know Zhou Yun had left.

238
00:18:46,193 --> 00:18:47,233
That means,

239
00:18:48,433 --> 00:18:52,072
she wanted to show she had nothing to do
with Zhou Yun leaving, right?

240
00:18:53,233 --> 00:18:55,352
Well, you're making some progress.

241
00:18:55,913 --> 00:18:56,952
I learned from the best.

242
00:18:57,632 --> 00:18:58,513
Bootlicker.

243
00:19:02,273 --> 00:19:05,473
Anyway, we need to talk
to Ge Wenjun first.

244
00:19:06,792 --> 00:19:08,984
Why would a parent

245
00:19:09,816 --> 00:19:14,112
of a student who has graduated
file a complaint about Zhou Yun?

246
00:19:16,913 --> 00:19:19,312
Zhou Yun? Who's that?

247
00:19:20,273 --> 00:19:22,193
Bai Shu's homeroom teacher
from middle school.

248
00:19:26,753 --> 00:19:27,632
I remember her.

249
00:19:28,504 --> 00:19:32,200
(2004, Qidaohezi)

250
00:19:53,112 --> 00:19:53,913
Ms. Zhou.

251
00:19:54,473 --> 00:19:55,592
Ma'am.

252
00:19:56,233 --> 00:19:57,312
What brings you here?

253
00:19:57,753 --> 00:20:01,193
Bai Shu hasn't been coming to class.
What happened to her?

254
00:20:02,112 --> 00:20:06,592
Bai Shu is sick.
I've requested leave from the school.

255
00:20:07,753 --> 00:20:09,832
Didn't the grade head inform you?

256
00:20:11,273 --> 00:20:12,152
I didn't know.

257
00:20:12,913 --> 00:20:16,673
The entrance exam is tomorrow.
I came here to check on her.

258
00:20:19,152 --> 00:20:22,033
She won't be taking the exam.
Thanks for your concern.

259
00:20:22,913 --> 00:20:25,513
Why? Is it just because of her health?

260
00:20:26,033 --> 00:20:29,713
She was doing so well.
It's a pity to miss the exam.

261
00:20:31,112 --> 00:20:33,632
Ma'am, I am her teacher.

262
00:20:33,753 --> 00:20:36,592
Please let me see my student,
no matter what.

263
00:20:45,792 --> 00:20:46,392
Fine.

264
00:20:49,072 --> 00:20:49,673
Please come in.

265
00:21:10,552 --> 00:21:11,233
Slippers, please.

266
00:21:11,713 --> 00:21:12,312
Thank you.

267
00:21:25,473 --> 00:21:26,072
Please sit.

268
00:22:07,112 --> 00:22:07,713
Come here.

269
00:22:09,152 --> 00:22:12,713
Bai Shu, are you okay?
Why did you cut your hair?

270
00:22:13,552 --> 00:22:14,592
It is too hot.

271
00:22:18,592 --> 00:22:20,792
I've graded your third mock exam paper.

272
00:22:21,112 --> 00:22:23,152
I'd like to point out
some mistakes of yours.

273
00:22:24,433 --> 00:22:27,112
Although I just found out
you won't take the exam.

274
00:22:27,792 --> 00:22:29,513
Do you still want me to show you?

275
00:22:29,713 --> 00:22:32,792
She's not even taking the exam.
Is this necessary?

276
00:22:35,033 --> 00:22:35,913
I-I want to know.

277
00:22:39,832 --> 00:22:42,392
Can I just go over them with her
in the living room?

278
00:22:44,513 --> 00:22:45,152
Please sit.

279
00:22:46,913 --> 00:22:47,413
Okay.

280
00:22:56,953 --> 00:22:58,352
I'll stay here with you.

281
00:22:59,673 --> 00:23:00,173
Alright?

282
00:23:13,233 --> 00:23:16,152
You shouldn't have made a mistake
on this question.

283
00:23:16,792 --> 00:23:19,473
This is clearly a distractor.

284
00:23:28,273 --> 00:23:29,193
I

285
00:23:33,552 --> 00:23:34,152
want to

286
00:23:36,233 --> 00:23:36,913
take

287
00:23:38,993 --> 00:23:40,152
the exam.

288
00:23:51,513 --> 00:23:52,513
Take

289
00:23:54,592 --> 00:23:55,273
me

290
00:23:57,152 --> 00:23:58,193
out.

291
00:24:06,112 --> 00:24:07,513
Did you have any issues with her?

292
00:24:15,713 --> 00:24:19,513
Was it her body
they found at Qidian Middle School?

293
00:24:21,632 --> 00:24:24,433
We can't disclose case details.
Please answer my question.

294
00:24:26,993 --> 00:24:28,273
Even if it really is her,

295
00:24:30,392 --> 00:24:31,552
I will tell the truth.

296
00:24:32,753 --> 00:24:33,513
I hate her.

297
00:24:35,953 --> 00:24:38,993
Because she destroyed my relationship
with my daughter.

298
00:24:40,033 --> 00:24:41,753
Bai Shu, come with me.

299
00:24:41,993 --> 00:24:43,473
Bai Shu, don't you dare come out.

300
00:24:43,733 --> 00:24:44,233
Bai Shu.

301
00:24:44,233 --> 00:24:44,792
Get out.

302
00:24:44,953 --> 00:24:46,632
You can't stop her from taking the exam.

303
00:24:46,713 --> 00:24:48,673
And you can't take my daughter away.

304
00:24:48,753 --> 00:24:49,392
- Out!
- Enough!

305
00:24:49,872 --> 00:24:52,233
Get out.

306
00:24:52,233 --> 00:24:52,872
Enough.

307
00:24:53,632 --> 00:24:54,152
Come with me.

308
00:24:56,513 --> 00:24:57,473
Bai Shu.

309
00:24:59,673 --> 00:25:04,473
Our Minors Protection Law stipulates
that minors have the right

310
00:25:05,152 --> 00:25:07,832
to receive an education
and take entrance exams.

311
00:25:08,872 --> 00:25:10,433
As Bai Shu's guardian,

312
00:25:10,753 --> 00:25:14,713
preventing her from taking the exam
is an illegal act.

313
00:25:14,713 --> 00:25:15,352
Understand?

314
00:25:16,433 --> 00:25:18,832
Why wouldn't I let her
take the high school entrance exam?

315
00:25:19,832 --> 00:25:22,953
I just wanted her to apologize,
then I would send her to the exam.

316
00:25:22,953 --> 00:25:23,832
She wouldn't be late.

317
00:25:24,913 --> 00:25:26,913
We were just about to reconcile.

318
00:25:27,513 --> 00:25:30,832
But Zhou Yun suddenly showed up
and threw a wrench in it.

319
00:25:32,112 --> 00:25:34,433
She thought she was a caring teacher,

320
00:25:34,673 --> 00:25:36,832
but really, she was just a busybody.

321
00:25:42,433 --> 00:25:43,513
Sorry, I lost my composure.

322
00:25:45,352 --> 00:25:48,872
I won't try to hide
my disgust and hatred for her.

323
00:25:50,513 --> 00:25:54,552
Zhou Yun had already left the school.
Why did you still report her?

324
00:25:55,312 --> 00:25:57,592
How would I know she had already left?

325
00:25:58,312 --> 00:25:59,872
Where she went, what she was doing,

326
00:26:01,112 --> 00:26:04,033
none of that had anything to do with me.

327
00:26:04,392 --> 00:26:06,792
So, did you have any evidence
when you reported her?

328
00:26:07,473 --> 00:26:10,993
I dared to use my real name.
What more evidence do you need?

329
00:26:20,713 --> 00:26:22,993
Thank you for your cooperation.
We're done for today.

330
00:26:23,433 --> 00:26:23,953
Let's go.

331
00:26:26,392 --> 00:26:27,733
Wait.

332
00:26:29,352 --> 00:26:31,433
Could you please not tell Bai Shu

333
00:26:32,832 --> 00:26:34,473
that I reported Zhou Yun?

334
00:26:35,112 --> 00:26:36,832
After all, she likes Zhou Yun.

335
00:26:37,792 --> 00:26:39,913
I don't want her to think badly of me.

336
00:26:41,913 --> 00:26:44,832
We have protocols.
Our conversations are confidential.

337
00:26:46,273 --> 00:26:47,832
Okay, thank you.

338
00:26:57,033 --> 00:27:00,473
Based on the current analysis,
Zhou Yun is very likely the deceased.

339
00:27:02,993 --> 00:27:04,433
It's still too early to say that.

340
00:27:05,673 --> 00:27:07,832
However, Zhou Yun
is definitely a key figure.

341
00:27:08,352 --> 00:27:11,713
Our top priority is to find her.

342
00:27:12,312 --> 00:27:12,812
Got it.

343
00:27:15,753 --> 00:27:18,152
(Zhou Yun was Bai Shu
and Ren Xiaoming's homeroom teacher.)

344
00:27:18,953 --> 00:27:22,993
(They were once such close friends,
but now they've lost contact.)

345
00:27:23,632 --> 00:27:26,193
(Their accounts of the diary
are worlds apart.)

346
00:27:26,872 --> 00:27:29,033
(One says it exists.
The other says it doesn't.)

347
00:27:29,552 --> 00:27:30,753
(What's going on?)

348
00:27:32,832 --> 00:27:36,193
(And Ge Wenjun makes no effort
to hide her dislike for Zhou Yun.)

349
00:27:37,433 --> 00:27:39,632
(Assuming the deceased is Zhou Yun,)

350
00:27:40,072 --> 00:27:42,753
(could Ge Wenjun be the murderer?)

351
00:27:45,792 --> 00:27:50,993
(If she is the killer, how could she
be so brazen in front of the police?)

352
00:27:52,072 --> 00:27:53,832
(Isn't she turning herself in?)

353
00:28:36,072 --> 00:28:36,592
Mom.

354
00:28:37,753 --> 00:28:38,792
What took you so long?

355
00:28:39,233 --> 00:28:41,993
I came as soon as I got your call.
And I brought a lawyer.

356
00:28:42,713 --> 00:28:44,392
Why didn't you keep an eye on him?

357
00:28:44,632 --> 00:28:47,152
You're blaming me?
It's all because of you.

358
00:28:47,632 --> 00:28:50,072
He saw the video of you
hitting Liu Xiaoran in the bookstore.

359
00:28:50,392 --> 00:28:51,473
Someone called you crazy.

360
00:28:51,473 --> 00:28:54,552
- That's how he got into a fight.
- Are you blaming me?

361
00:28:54,913 --> 00:28:56,392
Did I tell him to hit anyone?

362
00:28:56,832 --> 00:28:58,352
Didn't I come to handle the problem?

363
00:28:58,513 --> 00:29:01,273
Shouldn't you?
Don't forget how he got this illness.

364
00:29:03,592 --> 00:29:04,152
Come back.

365
00:29:04,953 --> 00:29:06,552
I'm not wanted here. You handle it.

366
00:29:06,753 --> 00:29:07,352
I can't.

367
00:29:07,352 --> 00:29:07,953
You handle it.

368
00:29:07,953 --> 00:29:08,592
You caused this.

369
00:29:08,913 --> 00:29:09,552
What can I do?

370
00:29:10,433 --> 00:29:12,352
He's locked up. He must be terrified.

371
00:29:12,513 --> 00:29:13,832
You must take care of him.

372
00:29:13,953 --> 00:29:16,433
What are you doing? You're in public.

373
00:29:18,033 --> 00:29:18,533
I...

374
00:29:19,352 --> 00:29:19,993
Sorry.

375
00:29:19,993 --> 00:29:20,913
What brings you here?

376
00:29:20,913 --> 00:29:21,993
Sorry about that.

377
00:29:23,832 --> 00:29:24,632
This is my mom.

378
00:29:25,753 --> 00:29:26,352
Hello, Auntie.

379
00:29:26,352 --> 00:29:28,832
Li Meng. Police officer.
My high school classmate.

380
00:29:30,433 --> 00:29:33,552
Why didn't you tell me
you had a police officer classmate?

381
00:29:34,673 --> 00:29:35,913
Li Meng, right?

382
00:29:35,913 --> 00:29:36,592
Yeah, Auntie.

383
00:29:36,592 --> 00:29:38,072
Can I add you on WeChat?

384
00:29:38,072 --> 00:29:38,832
Mom.

385
00:29:38,913 --> 00:29:39,552
Sure.

386
00:29:40,112 --> 00:29:41,112
I'll scan your QR code.

387
00:29:42,352 --> 00:29:43,552
My son is in there.

388
00:29:43,832 --> 00:29:44,392
What happened?

389
00:29:44,913 --> 00:29:45,513
He hit someone.

390
00:29:45,753 --> 00:29:46,312
It's nothing.

391
00:29:47,673 --> 00:29:50,513
He had a conflict with someone.
The lawyer is handling it.

392
00:29:50,513 --> 00:29:51,312
Go back to work.

393
00:29:51,673 --> 00:29:52,993
Wait.

394
00:29:52,993 --> 00:29:54,433
Auntie, it's uncomfortable here.

395
00:29:54,632 --> 00:29:57,072
Huang, take her to our reception room.

396
00:29:57,193 --> 00:29:58,753
Bring her a pot of fine tea.

397
00:29:58,872 --> 00:29:59,552
- Got it.
- Go ahead.

398
00:29:59,632 --> 00:30:00,673
- Thank you.
- Okay.

399
00:30:00,673 --> 00:30:03,033
- This way, please.
- Talk to your classmate.

400
00:30:03,033 --> 00:30:04,473
Catch up.

401
00:30:04,792 --> 00:30:05,352
Auntie.

402
00:30:05,352 --> 00:30:05,913
Rest assured.

403
00:30:05,913 --> 00:30:06,832
- Here.
- Okay.

404
00:30:09,792 --> 00:30:11,552
- Let's go.
- Let's catch up.

405
00:30:11,753 --> 00:30:12,433
Sorry about that.

406
00:30:12,552 --> 00:30:13,152
It's nothing.

407
00:30:19,913 --> 00:30:20,513
Come on in.

408
00:30:22,112 --> 00:30:24,233
Is this where you interrogate criminals?

409
00:30:25,913 --> 00:30:29,392
That's the interrogation room.
This is just a mediation room.

410
00:30:30,473 --> 00:30:32,913
Like neighbor disputes,
couples fighting.

411
00:30:33,233 --> 00:30:37,233
Police officers bring them here
to talk things out

412
00:30:38,033 --> 00:30:39,673
and solve the problems peacefully.

413
00:30:40,913 --> 00:30:45,552
You wouldn't be allowed
in the interrogation room.

414
00:30:46,872 --> 00:30:47,433
Sit.

415
00:30:49,392 --> 00:30:50,456
My phone...

416
00:30:50,456 --> 00:30:51,713
Just put it anywhere.

417
00:30:54,033 --> 00:30:56,233
I kind of wanted to get a feel for it.

418
00:30:56,392 --> 00:30:57,673
For what?

419
00:30:58,993 --> 00:31:01,792
Confess. Tell me everything you know.

420
00:31:08,713 --> 00:31:10,273
You even know that?

421
00:31:10,673 --> 00:31:13,552
Isn't that what you guys say
when questioning criminals?

422
00:31:13,552 --> 00:31:14,913
That's what they do in TV dramas.

423
00:31:15,352 --> 00:31:18,392
You want to know
how we interrogate criminals?

424
00:31:20,072 --> 00:31:20,632
Can I?

425
00:31:22,513 --> 00:31:24,013
Sure, let's give it a try.

426
00:31:24,233 --> 00:31:24,832
Okay.

427
00:31:30,513 --> 00:31:33,433
Ren Xiaoming,
describe your crime in detail.

428
00:31:35,312 --> 00:31:36,072
How did she die?

429
00:31:38,513 --> 00:31:39,416
Why'd you kill her?

430
00:31:52,152 --> 00:31:53,673
What's wrong with you?

431
00:31:56,033 --> 00:31:57,673
My palms are sweating.

432
00:31:58,312 --> 00:31:59,152
Did I scare you?

433
00:32:00,152 --> 00:32:03,392
You know, the vibe you give off
is really something else.

434
00:32:03,913 --> 00:32:04,592
Of course.

435
00:32:06,753 --> 00:32:08,632
Is everything okay with your brother?

436
00:32:08,913 --> 00:32:09,953
You don't need help?

437
00:32:10,352 --> 00:32:11,913
It's fine. He's always like this.

438
00:32:13,033 --> 00:32:16,233
I almost didn't get into high school
because of him.

439
00:32:17,392 --> 00:32:19,592
Mr. Sun found a doctor for Xiaofei.

440
00:32:20,433 --> 00:32:24,033
(2004, Qidaohezi)
An expert from Qingzhou, very famous.

441
00:32:25,033 --> 00:32:26,072
I don't want a doctor.

442
00:32:26,273 --> 00:32:27,033
What do you know?

443
00:32:27,953 --> 00:32:29,832
This expert is coming here on Wednesday.

444
00:32:30,473 --> 00:32:31,928
Mr. Sun has something else to do.

445
00:32:32,072 --> 00:32:35,552
Take half a day off,
and we'll take Xiaofei there.

446
00:32:36,152 --> 00:32:40,592
Fine, I don't need to ask for leave
for the high school entrance exam.

447
00:32:41,152 --> 00:32:42,152
I just won't go.

448
00:32:43,913 --> 00:32:44,953
It's on Wednesday?

449
00:32:46,273 --> 00:32:49,433
And you call yourself a parent?
You don't even know when the exam is.

450
00:32:50,913 --> 00:32:53,273
What's so special about it?
Why should I remember the date?

451
00:32:53,673 --> 00:32:55,273
Does the world revolve around you?

452
00:32:55,392 --> 00:32:57,673
Why should the world
revolve around Xiaofei?

453
00:32:57,792 --> 00:32:59,544
Why should I take him to see the doctor?

454
00:32:59,673 --> 00:33:00,352
I'm not going.

455
00:33:00,632 --> 00:33:01,592
Fine, don't go then.

456
00:33:01,713 --> 00:33:02,213
Really?

457
00:33:02,312 --> 00:33:02,953
Not you.

458
00:33:03,352 --> 00:33:05,433
Don't go then.
Why are you throwing a tantrum?

459
00:33:06,632 --> 00:33:08,832
Selfish. Let's see how well you do.

460
00:33:09,513 --> 00:33:10,033
Let's eat.

461
00:33:20,832 --> 00:33:21,352
Come and eat.

462
00:33:22,312 --> 00:33:22,953
I'm not eating.

463
00:33:24,552 --> 00:33:25,913
I need to study.

464
00:33:31,112 --> 00:33:31,753
Come and eat.

465
00:33:37,312 --> 00:33:38,584
We're distributing the papers.

466
00:33:39,312 --> 00:33:42,152
Pages one to four. Check them.

467
00:33:48,673 --> 00:33:50,392
Ma'am, Bai Shu is almost here.

468
00:33:50,832 --> 00:33:52,193
Check your papers. No talking.

469
00:33:57,624 --> 00:34:00,033
(Exam Subject: Mathematics, Pages 1-4)

470
00:34:00,033 --> 00:34:01,513
The exam begins.

471
00:34:06,713 --> 00:34:07,832
Ma'am, she's almost here.

472
00:34:07,832 --> 00:34:09,672
Why do you keep worrying about others?

473
00:34:15,513 --> 00:34:18,313
Excuse me, sir.
I am this student's homeroom teacher.

474
00:34:32,552 --> 00:34:36,192
She's allowed to enter
within fifteen minutes of the start.

475
00:34:38,072 --> 00:34:38,632
Come in.

476
00:34:39,192 --> 00:34:39,712
Come on.

477
00:34:42,913 --> 00:34:44,433
Check pages one to four.

478
00:34:45,072 --> 00:34:46,552
Bai Shu, why did you cut your hair?

479
00:34:47,033 --> 00:34:49,072
Quiet. Take the exam.

480
00:35:14,712 --> 00:35:19,622
(A Hundred Days of Struggle,
A Dream Fulfilled in One Day)

481
00:35:19,622 --> 00:35:24,033
(Excellent Performance
in the High School Entrance Exam)

482
00:35:24,033 --> 00:35:24,712
Bai Shu.

483
00:35:30,473 --> 00:35:31,313
You cut your hair?

484
00:35:34,752 --> 00:35:35,672
It looks nice.

485
00:35:41,072 --> 00:35:43,672
- That night...
- That night, I went to sleep early

486
00:35:44,712 --> 00:35:45,848
and didn't go find you.

487
00:35:47,752 --> 00:35:48,984
How did you do on the exam?

488
00:35:50,112 --> 00:35:50,833
Not bad.

489
00:35:53,072 --> 00:35:55,232
Go home for lunch.
We have another exam this afternoon.

490
00:35:57,353 --> 00:35:58,433
What about you?

491
00:35:59,192 --> 00:36:01,913
Someone's picking me up. Go ahead.

492
00:36:04,152 --> 00:36:06,272
She's not here yet.
Let me keep you company.

493
00:36:06,272 --> 00:36:06,772
No need.

494
00:36:08,272 --> 00:36:09,033
Go ahead.

495
00:36:12,033 --> 00:36:12,533
Go on.

496
00:36:31,793 --> 00:36:33,672
(Why is Bai Shu with Ms. Zhou?)

497
00:36:50,433 --> 00:36:53,313
For all three days of the exam,
Ms. Zhou was there for Bai Shu.

498
00:36:54,353 --> 00:36:56,473
I thought it was strange.

499
00:36:57,592 --> 00:37:01,232
How could Ge Wenjun
let someone else pick up Bai Shu?

500
00:37:02,232 --> 00:37:03,712
Ms. Zhou was also acting strangely.

501
00:37:04,272 --> 00:37:07,752
She cared about me so much,
but she barely even spoke to me.

502
00:37:08,513 --> 00:37:11,752
She didn't even ask me
how I did on the exams.

503
00:37:12,072 --> 00:37:13,712
She just stayed by Bai Shu's side.

504
00:37:14,513 --> 00:37:15,513
I didn't know why.

505
00:37:16,152 --> 00:37:18,473
But I felt like they were avoiding me.

506
00:37:20,472 --> 00:37:22,932
(A Hundred Days of Struggle,
A Dream Fulfilled in One Day)

507
00:37:22,932 --> 00:37:25,393
(Excellent Performance
in the High School Entrance Exam)

508
00:37:25,393 --> 00:37:25,993
Xiaoming.

509
00:37:29,712 --> 00:37:30,993
Someone's picking you up again?

510
00:37:31,712 --> 00:37:33,933
Last subject this afternoon. Good luck.

511
00:37:35,793 --> 00:37:36,473
You too.

512
00:37:40,473 --> 00:37:41,232
How did it go?

513
00:37:42,192 --> 00:37:42,793
Not bad.

514
00:37:47,512 --> 00:37:53,672
(La City High School Entrance Exam
Qidaohezi Middle School Exam Site)

515
00:37:53,672 --> 00:37:54,393
Xiaofei. Xiaofei.

516
00:37:54,393 --> 00:37:54,913
That kid

517
00:37:54,913 --> 00:37:55,833
- is acting up again.
- Open up.

518
00:37:55,833 --> 00:37:56,473
Let me in.

519
00:37:56,473 --> 00:37:57,112
Oh dear.

520
00:37:57,833 --> 00:37:59,072
It's okay, Granny Sun.

521
00:37:59,072 --> 00:37:59,833
It's okay.

522
00:38:01,192 --> 00:38:02,473
I can't take it.

523
00:38:02,913 --> 00:38:04,272
I don't need your help.

524
00:38:04,552 --> 00:38:05,513
He can manage himself.

525
00:38:05,953 --> 00:38:07,072
