Please don't call the police.

529
00:38:15,632 --> 00:38:16,632
Please don't.

530
00:38:21,473 --> 00:38:23,913
He listens to his sister. Go back.

531
00:38:23,913 --> 00:38:26,433
Thank you for caring about Xiaofei.

532
00:38:26,433 --> 00:38:27,393
