- Xiaoming.

533
00:38:28,712 --> 00:38:31,313
Stay back.

534
00:38:31,592 --> 00:38:33,413
They're fine.

535
00:38:34,833 --> 00:38:35,632
Ren Xiaofei.

536
00:38:35,632 --> 00:38:36,504
Stay back.

