547
00:39:15,552 --> 00:39:16,473
Don't touch me.

548
00:39:16,552 --> 00:39:17,592
Get the medicine.

549
00:39:17,833 --> 00:39:18,793
Don't touch me.

550
00:39:18,953 --> 00:39:19,793
Have some water.

551
00:39:21,552 --> 00:39:22,973
Have some water.

552
00:39:23,353 --> 00:39:25,192
Have some water.

553
00:39:26,712 --> 00:39:28,953
Come on, open your mouth.

554
00:39:30,112 --> 00:39:30,840
Take it away.

555
00:39:31,793 --> 00:39:34,993
Good boy.

556
00:39:35,552 --> 00:39:37,473
Good boy.

557
00:39:48,413 --> 00:39:48,913
Go home.

558
00:39:48,913 --> 00:39:49,632
Go home.

559
00:39:50,393 --> 00:39:51,072
Go home.

560
00:39:51,793 --> 00:39:52,833
Mom's here.

561
00:39:52,833 --> 00:39:54,933
Mom's here.

562
00:39:55,033 --> 00:39:55,913
It's okay.

563
00:39:55,993 --> 00:39:57,072
Mom's here.

564
00:39:57,072 --> 00:39:58,393
