572
00:40:54,632 --> 00:40:55,132
I'm fine.

573
00:40:55,672 --> 00:40:56,393
Focus on the exam.

574
00:41:25,993 --> 00:41:27,033
Are you alright?

575
00:41:28,353 --> 00:41:29,464
